EventItems.EventItemTitle: An Ordinance to Amend Section 5.16.3.G, 5.20.10 and 5.30.1 of Chapter 55 (Unified Development Code) of Title V of the Code of the City of Ann Arbor (Marijuana Licenses, Trees in the Right-of-Way, Landscape Modifications) (ORD-22-xx)

EventItems.EventItemActionText:
A motion was made by Councilmember Disch, seconded by Councilmember Hayner, that the Ordinance be amended as follows:

Section G. 3. of the Marijuana Ordinance 
e. All activities of a Marijuana Facility shall be conducted indoors. 
EXCEPTION:  CURBSIDE PICKUP MAY BE PROVIDED FOR ANY MARIJUANA PROVISIONING CENTER, MARIJUANA RETAILER, OR MARIJUANA MICROBUSINESS.

On a voice vote, the Mayor declared the motion carried.
